Summary: I saw in the sky a very unusual object
divs: Sighting DetailsI saw a silver disk in the air low on the horizon. I ran to get my camera and when I was able to take the pictures it was higher in the sky. When I first saw it I was immediatly interested in it as it was very unusual. It moved in an erratic pattern back and forth in th sky and lasted about 10 min total. Since I work in the aviation industry I am aware of the normal ways that aircraft behave and this did not behave in that way. Photos were facing an easterly direction,
